# 2p_sync — client. Stationary observer; screenshots at the same
# ticks as the host so the host's mech can be compared at
# matching moments.
#
# After P03 (with double-precision render clock + 8-entry snapshot
# ring), the client's view of the host's mech should track the
# host's actual pelvis position to within a few px (~100 ms interp
# delay = 1-2 px at run speed, ~15 px at jet speed).

window 1280 720
out build/shots/net/sync_client
network connect 127.0.0.1:24061
name ClientB

at 200 shot pre_jet
at 240 shot mid_jet_up
at 280 shot peak
at 320 shot falling
at 360 shot mid_jet_down
at 400 shot landed
at 700 shot after
at 750 end
